OL,5, Tens of millions of pounds belonging to
OL,6, about 80,000 young people without      
OL,7, capacity to make financial decisions   
OL,8, could be locked in trust funds, a      
OL,9, report suggests.                       
OL,11,FThose families must go through court to
OL,12,Faccess the savings when accounts mature
OL,13,F- a process which can take months and  
OL,14,Fcost hundreds of pounds.               
OL,16,FOnly 15 accounts were accessed this way
OL,17,Fin 2021. The government says it is     
OL,18,Funable to share more recent figures.   
OL,20,FIt says it is trying to speed up cases.
